products.title: Martenaa Baby & Toddler Milk Bottle Set – 4-Piece Maternal and Baby Feeding Products | Durable, Safe & Easy-to-Clean Essentials for Everyday Use
products.body_html:
Martenaa Baby & Toddler Milk Bottle Set – 4-Piece Maternal and Baby Feeding Products combines safe materials, durable craftsmanship, and easy-to-clean design to provide the perfect solution for everyday feeding. This thoughtfully created set is designed to support both parents and little ones through every stage of early development while making feeding simpler, safer, and more enjoyable.

Smart Design Features

  • Durable BPA-Free Construction ensures long-lasting and safe daily use
  • 4-Piece Complete Set offers essential bottles for growing infants and toddlers
  • Ergonomic Standard Neck Design supports comfortable feeding and easy grip for parents
  • 280mL Capacity sized for newborns through toddlers’ feeding needs
  • Easy-to-Clean Material supports sterilization, rinsing, and dishwasher use
  • Leak-Resistant Cap & Secure Seal prevent spills during travel and storage

Setup and Usage

  1. Sterilize all bottles and nipples before first use
  2. Fill with breastmilk, formula, or liquids as needed
  3. Securely attach nipple and cap to prevent leaks
  4. Clean thoroughly after each feeding with warm water and mild soap
  5. Store bottles in a clean, dry space until next use

  • Bottle Capacity: 280mL each
  • Set Includes: 4 bottles with nipples and secure caps
  • Style: Standard mouth with ergonomic grip
  • Suitable for: Infants and toddlers, newborn to weaning stage

  •  Safe and BPA-free construction protects your baby’s health
  • Durable bottles built to withstand daily use and repeated cleaning
  • Complete set provides great value for busy parents
  • Easy-to-clean, dishwasher-safe design saves time and effort
  • Leak-resistant seal makes it perfect for both home and travel use

products.title: WobbleBub Baby Suction Bowl Set – Temperature-Sensing Spoon & Feeding Tableware for Infants
products.body_html:
• Make mealtime safe, fun, and worry-free with the WobbleBub Baby Suction Bowl Set. Designed for infants and toddlers, this innovative feeding set features strong suction bowls that prevent spills and a temperature-sensing spoon to ensure food is always at the perfect, safe temperature.

    Made from BPA-free, food-grade silicone, the set is gentle on your baby’s gums and safe for everyday use. Perfect for complementary foods, cereals, purees, and snacks, it is easy to clean, lightweight, and portable for feeding at home or on-the-go.

    Key Features:

    • Temperature-Sensing Spoon: Alerts you if food is too hot.

    • Strong Suction Bowls: Prevent spills and messes during feeding.

    • Safe & BPA-Free: Made from food-grade silicone.

    • Perfect for Infants: Ideal for cereals, purees, and snacks.

    • Easy to Clean & Portable: Dishwasher safe and travel-friendly.

    Enjoy mess-free, safe, and comfortable feeding times with the WobbleBub Baby Suction Bowl Set.
